  - printk logging mechanism;
  - Workqueue subsystem;
  - Memory management;
  - B.A.T.M.A.N. meshing protocol;
  - Bluetooth subsystem;
  - IPv4 networking;
  - IPv6 networking;
  - MAC80211 subsystem;
  - Multipath TCP;
